[0.007294, "o", "=============================================================\r\nScenario 62: pm qa regression replaces pm tui test\r\n=============================================================\r\n\r\n## Triple 1: three invocations (claude killed by timeout; we only need the logged prompt)\r\n\r\n-- pm qa regression smoke --\r\n"]
